tip.text: Durian mousse. Wished I can lick the bowl. (ahem) Its that good!
First time having Rainbow cake and Medzs version doesn't disappoint at all. Their red velvet cake is pretty good, although personally I don't like the chocs in the middle.
Cheap High Tea Set.. But overall i wouldnt really recommend it other than for its price. Good place to hang out tho.
Must try Deep Fried Mushrooms! Big portions for fish n chips. Thumbs down for portobello mushrooms. Bbq pork ribs too dry. Chef's Challenge buffalo wings arent tt spicy.
Squid Ink Pasta is awful. Pizza is just so-so. Tomato soup is wayyy too salty.
Low Cal Food: Avocado & Bacon Panini. Hot Chocolate <3
Go for the green curry chicken & pad thai! Tom Yum Clear Soup is mehh..
